title: Bachman Turner Overdrive - Gold (Flac) [FrankFoo]
description:
Bachman Turner Overdrive Gold (2005) (Flac)

Includes: Vorbis Tags & Front Cover

Info:
Editorial Reviews
Gold features the radio hits and album highlights from BTO's best-selling Mercury albums of the 70s.Includes the newly digitally remastered classics 'Gimme Your Money Please', 'Blue Collar', 'Takin' Care Of Business', 'Let It Ride', 'You Ain't Seen Nothing Yet', 'Roll On Down The Highway', 'Take It Like A Man', and 'Lookin' Out For #1'. Island. 2005.
